{
  "stem": "15396.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was on the-- for some reason, I don't know why, they wanted me to dub-- you know what dubbing is?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They wanted me to direct the dubbing of the film, a Canadian company, but it was a French film with [INAUDIBLE] and I've forgotten who else.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I asked them, I said, what's dubbing?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I should have told them, shouldn't I?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyway, they hired me, and I did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had an old Citroen at that time, but I would always take the bus so I could work on the dialogue while I was going back and forth to the studio.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I ran into a-- there was a famous painter from Romania named Stoenescu, and his son, Dan Stoenescu, was living in Paris.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, I'm going to have dinner with the most glamorous woman in Paris.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You want to come with me?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, no, I can't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've got to get up in the morning early.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was when the buses, you know, were open on the back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was raining, and I saw him passing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stopped for a red light, and I saw him passing to go to see this lady.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I thought, what the hell?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just as the bus pulled out, I jumped off and went with him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then eventually, we married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And here it is, she is a-- she was a German, and here my feeling about the Germans were so incredible.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But her mother had been very badly treated by the Nazis because she wouldn't stand up when-- she was a little girl then-- wouldn't stand up when Hitler came into the room.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so they knew what the family's--",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
